[[=]]
++ **Addenda: 3580.7:**
[[/=]]
----
SCP-3580 currently remains at large.

The chasm created during the prior incident revealed a large underground temple-like structure, filled with overgrowth of various unidentified species of flora as well as a plethora of glowing gold thaumaturgic symbols. A review of both the current state of this place, as well as compiled THETA footage, revealed that a large structure in its center appears to now be missing.

Ongoing Veil protection operations are in effect. Despite this, however, international tensions have risen between Germany and Türkiye, with Germany claiming that Türkiye had stolen the Bagger 288, and Türkiye claiming that Germany had invaded its territory and planted the vehicle there being heavily debated in international courts. The Foundation has opted to deny all claims of its involvement during this time until a working explanation can be devised.

A memorial for all personnel killed during this incident will take place on the 28th. All of these agents have been individually awarded with Foundation Stars of Bravery.
----
The following message was sent to all personnel assigned to Project Labyrinth from a Foundation terminal in New Zealand.

@@ @@

